//   kernel_sources.hpp/cpp  - kernel .cpp files, looked up individually by name
//   kernel_includes.hpp/cpp - kernel .h/.hpp headers, provided in bulk to HIPRTC
//
// The .hpp/.cpp split keeps the large embedded string literals compiled once in
// the .cpp; the .hpp exposes only extern declarations and lookup signatures.
//
